latestIgtvVideos.title: Brinda Shah shares her workout experience with OTF
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Experience MORE LIFE with OTF. • @brindaashah When it comes to the enjoyment aspect of my workout, I’ve found a place I love working at @otfmumbai @orangetheory and this is something I hope everyone has or finds this year because I think it’s so important when it comes to establishing a long-term fitness routine! 
Orangetheory is a science-backed, technology-tracked, coach-inspired group workout designed to produce results from the inside out. Their workouts are designed for everyone and there are three different type of paces you can go for which is power walkers, joggers, runners. 
Workout is partly cardio based and partly weight training 
60 mins and there is a professional fitness coach in the studio who will help you reach you achieve your fitness goals! 
Those who plan to start a fitness routine at @orangetheory @otfmumbai You can grab a special discount with my name (Brinda) and along with that First class will be Free for you. 
Studio number is 1800 266 3116! 🎥: @nickhill_shinde_photography
